Williston State College's Montana Schneider goes for the kill against a Bismarck State College double-block during Wednesday's game at The Well. (Matt Hickman • Williston Herald) 
Williston State College blockers Alycia McGloughlin, right and Lexie Rumpel successful turn back a Bismarck State hit Wednesday night. (Matt Hickman • Williston Herald)
